'''市场支配地位'''（{{lang-en|'''market dominance'''}}）描述的是一个公司能够控制[[市场|市场]]的情况。<ref>{{Cite book |last=Rosenbaum |first=David Ira |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=htQDB-Pf4VIC&dq=Market+Dominance:+How+Firms+Gain,+Hold,+or+Lose+It+and+the+Impact+on+Economic+Performance&pg=PP7 |title=Market Dominance: How Firms Gain, Hold, Or Lose it and the Impact on Economic Performance |date=1998 |publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group |isbn=978-0-275-95604-2 |language=en}}</ref>一个占支配地位的公司拥有影响[[竞争_(经济学)|竞争]]<ref>{{Cite book |last=Shepherd |first=William |title=The Economics of Industrial Organisation |publisher=Englewood Cliffs |year=1990 |location=NJ |pages=273=0}}</ref>和影响市场[[价格|价格]]的权力。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Doyle |first=Chris |date=20-22 November 2002 |title=Market Definition and Dominance |url=https://www.itu.int/osg/spu/ni/competition/Presentations/Market%20Definition%20-CDoyle.pdf}}</ref>一个公司的支配地位是衡量一个[[品牌|品牌]]、[[产品|产品]]、[[服务|服务]]或[[法人团体|公司]]相对于竞争产品的{{link-en|市场力量|Market power}}，据此，一个占支配地位的公司可以独立于其[[竞争对手|竞争对手]]或[[消费者|消费者]]，<ref>{{Cite web |title=What does dominant market position mean? Is it acceptable? {{!}} Department of Economics |url=https://www.econ.iastate.edu/ask-an-economist/what-does-dominant-market-position-mean-it-acceptable |access-date=2022-05-02 |website=www.econ.iastate.edu}}</ref>并且不关心资源分配。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Market Dominance: How Firms Gain, Hold, or Lose It and the Impact on Economic Performance |url=https://eh.net/book_reviews/market-dominance-how-firms-gain-hold-or-lose-it-and-the-impact-on-economic-performance/ |access-date=2022-05-02 |website=eh.net}}</ref>支配地位既是一个[[法律|法律]]概念也是一个[[经济|经济]]概念，在确定一个公司的市场地位是否为支配地位时，这两者的区别很重要。

